snippet: Officials are waiting for preliminary tests on two farms in Wright County to be confirmed.
abstract: Iowa agriculture officials say bird flu will affect another four million egg-laying chickens on two more farms in country already afflicted with disease.
lead_paragraph: Officials are waiting for preliminary tests on two farms in Wright County to be confirmed.

headline.print_headline: Iowa Says 4 Million More Chickens Have Bird Flu
